xport</span> _colcon_cd_root=/opt/ros/foxy/</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">source</span> /usr/share/colcon_argcomplete/hook/colcon-argcomplete.zsh</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">eval</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"subst\">$(register-python-argcomplete3 ros2)</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">eval</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;<span class=\"subst\">$(register-python-argcomplete3 colcon)</span>&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"后记\"><a href=\"#后记\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"后记\"></a>后记</h2><p>看着内容不多，但在搜索引擎里面找这些废了不少功夫，所以就写了这个，方便自己也方便别人。</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"X3PI","path":"api/tags/X3PI.json"}]}